@BelCantoBhoy Dear Barry,
I am very sorry to hear about your experience. I kindly ask you to please send an official complaint to our Customer Relations. Please use the contact form on our website https://t.co/99riI0OUuT.
Kind Regards, Alessandra

@Lorna45665505 Hi Lorna,
I'm sorry to hear that. The Social Media Team does not have access to the baggage system. Please get in touch with the phone number on your lost baggage report or you can check the status of your baggage online via this link https://t.co/hrzpeJ2rHC 
Best regards, Alessa

@n_bagheri45 Hello,
we're sorry to hear your bag has been delayed. Our Baggage team will do all they can to reunite you with it as soon as possible. 
Best regards, Alessandra

@kibristurku Hi there, 
As it turns out all corona-related entry regulations have been lifted since 01.06.22. We wish you a pleasant flight.
Best regards, Shawn

@ggordan Hi there, 
Thank you for getting in touch. Please send us your booking code via PM, so we can take a closer look.
Best regards, Shawn

@alimasonne Hi there,
We are sorry that you had difficulty contacting us by phone. Due to the current situation, unfortunately, all our channels are overloaded and there may be longer waiting times. Please let us know if there is anything we can assist you with?
Best regards, Shawn

@Victori45276683 Hi there, 
We are sorry for all the inconvenience. Please check your inbox, as we have replied to your DM. 
Best regards, Shawn

@zmwaki1 Hello,
please send us your booking code so we can have a closer look at your reservation.
Best regards, Alessandra
